(7, 'vi', 74, 1, 1, 0, 0, 'Chủ nhân huy chương Vàng Vật lý mê thể thao', 'chu-nhan-huy-chuong-vang-vat-ly-me-the-thao', '', '{"introimage":"26","list_suggest":"","fulltext":"<h2 class=\\"Lead\\">K&iacute;nh c\\u1eadn, th&ocirc;ng minh, h\\u1ecdc gi\\u1ecfi nh\\u01b0ng kh&ocirc;ng ph\\u1ea3i m\\u1ecdt  s&aacute;ch, gi&agrave;nh nhi\\u1ec1u th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch v\\u1ec1 th\\u1ec3 thao l&agrave; ch&acirc;n dung c\\u1ee7a L&ecirc; Huy Quang  (THPT chuy&ecirc;n Lam S\\u01a1n, Thanh H&oacute;a), ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi v\\u1eeba gi&agrave;nh huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng V&agrave;ng  Olympic V\\u1eadt l&yacute; ch&acirc;u &Aacute;.<br \\/>&gt; <a class=\\"Lead\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/xa-hoi\\/giao-duc\\/2012\\/05\\/viet-nam-xep-thu-tu-cuoc-thi-olympic-vat-ly-chau-a\\/\\">Vi\\u1ec7t Nam x\\u1ebfp th\\u1ee9 t\\u01b0 cu\\u1ed9c thi Olympic V\\u1eadt l&yacute; ch&acirc;u &Aacute;<\\/a><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Nheo m\\u1eaft sau c\\u1eb7p k&iacute;nh c\\u1eadn r\\u1ed3i n\\u1edf n\\u1ee5 c\\u01b0\\u1eddi t\\u01b0\\u01a1i r&oacute;i,  \\"ch&agrave;ng trai v&agrave;ng\\" c\\u1ee7a V\\u1eadt l&yacute; Vi\\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\\u1ebft, \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 cao  trong c&aacute;c k\\u1ef3 thi, c\\u1eadu ch\\u1ec9 c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t th\\u1ee9 v\\u0169 kh&iacute;, \\u0111&oacute; l&agrave; s\\u1ef1 quy\\u1ebft t&acirc;m. \\"N\\u0103m  ngo&aacute;i d\\u1ef1 thi v&agrave; ch\\u1ec9 gi&agrave;nh huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110\\u1ed3ng, em ch\\u01b0a h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng v&agrave; quy\\u1ebft t&acirc;m  h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ed5i m&agrave;u huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng. Nh\\u01b0ng em kh&ocirc;ng h\\u1ecdc theo ki\\u1ec3u m\\u1ecdt s&aacute;ch, em  v\\u1eeba h\\u1ecdc v&agrave; v\\u1eeba ch\\u01a1i, ph&acirc;n b\\u1ed5 th\\u1eddi gian h\\u1ee3p l&yacute;\\", Quang n&oacute;i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Quang chia s\\u1ebb, h\\u1ecdc ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c t\\u1eeb nhi\\u1ec1u t&agrave;i li\\u1ec7u, c\\u1ed9ng  v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 gi&uacute;p s\\u1ee9c c\\u1ee7a th\\u1ea7y c&ocirc; v&agrave; l&uacute;c h\\u1ecdc c\\u1eadu t\\u1eadp trung tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i. Bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1ed1i  Quang ch\\u1ec9 h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u1ebfn 22h30, sau \\u0111&oacute; xu\\u1ed1ng nh&agrave; xem tivi r\\u1ed3i \\u0111i ng\\u1ee7. \\"Em  kh&ocirc;ng h\\u1ecdc th&acirc;u \\u0111&ecirc;m. Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng&agrave;y \\u0111i thi Olympic m\\u1ed9t tu\\u1ea7n em ch\\u1ec9 \\u0103n v&agrave; ng\\u1ee7  v&igrave; s\\u1ee3 h\\u1ecdc nhi\\u1ec1u s\\u1ebd lo\\u1ea1n m\\u1ea5t\\", ch&agrave;ng trai v&agrave;ng b\\u1eadt m&iacute;.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Ng&agrave;y nh\\u1ecf, m\\u1ed7i khi b\\u1ed1 \\u0111i \\u0111&aacute;nh c\\u1ea7u l&ocirc;ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u01b0a Quang \\u0111i  theo. L&acirc;u d\\u1ea7n Quang th\\u1ea5y y&ecirc;u m&ocirc;n th\\u1ec3 thao n&agrave;y, c\\u1ee9 sau gi\\u1edd h\\u1ecdc chi\\u1ec1u c\\u1eadu  l\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea7m v\\u1ee3t ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u1ebfn g\\u1ea7n 19h t\\u1ed1i. Ngo&agrave;i ra, Quang c&ograve;n r\\u1ea5t th&iacute;ch \\u0111&aacute; c\\u1ea7u.  R\\u1ea3nh r\\u1ed7i, c\\u1eadu t\\u1eadp h\\u1ee3p nh&oacute;m b\\u1ea1n c&ugrave;ng ch\\u01a1i. V\\u1edbi Quang, ch\\u01a1i th\\u1ec3 thao l&agrave;  c&aacute;ch t\\u1ea1o s\\u1ef1 s\\u1ea3ng kho&aacute;i, l\\u1ea5y l\\u1ea1i th\\u01b0 th&aacute;i sau m\\u1ed9t ng&agrave;y mi\\u1ec7t m&agrave;i h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">N\\u0103m l\\u1edbp 7, Quang d\\u1ef1 h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph&ugrave; \\u0110\\u1ed5ng th&agrave;nh ph\\u1ed1 m&ocirc;n \\u0111&aacute;  c\\u1ea7u v&agrave; gi&agrave;nh gi\\u1ea3i 3. L\\u1edbp 12, c\\u0169ng \\u1edf h\\u1ed9i thi n&agrave;y c\\u1eadu gi&agrave;nh gi\\u1ea3i khuy\\u1ebfn  kh&iacute;ch m&ocirc;n c\\u1ea7u l&ocirc;ng. Th\\u1ea7y Kim Ng\\u1ecdc Ch&iacute;nh, Hi\\u1ec7u tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng THPT chuy&ecirc;n Lam S\\u01a1n  cho bi\\u1ebft, \\u1edf tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Quang kh&ocirc;ng ch\\u1ec9 n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng v\\u1ec1 th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp, s\\u1ef1  th&ocirc;ng minh m&agrave; c&ograve;n gi\\u1ecfi c&aacute;c m&ocirc;n th\\u1ec3 thao.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">\\"V\\u1eeba qua, khi \\u0111i thi h\\u1ecdc sinh gi\\u1ecfi qu\\u1ed1c gia v\\u1ec1, Quang  c&ograve;n d\\u1ef1 thi c\\u1ea7u l&ocirc;ng to&agrave;n tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng nh&acirc;n k\\u1ef7 ni\\u1ec7m 26\\/3 v&agrave; gi&agrave;nh gi\\u1ea3i nh\\u1ea5t. Em  c&ograve;n l&agrave; h\\u1ecdc sinh b\\u01a1i l\\u1ed9i r\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t\\", th\\u1ea7y Ch&iacute;nh t\\u1ef1 h&agrave;o n&oacute;i v\\u1ec1 h\\u1ecdc tr&ograve;.<\\/p>\\r\\n<table border=\\"0\\" cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"3\\" width=\\"1\\" align=\\"center\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/Files\\/Subject\\/3b\\/bd\\/68\\/dc\\/quang_2.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"495\\" height=\\"357\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\"Image\\">Quang cho bi\\u1ebft v\\u0169 kh&iacute; \\u0111\\u1ec3 l&agrave;m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c m\\u1ecdi vi\\u1ec7c l&agrave; s\\u1ef1 quy\\u1ebft t&acirc;m. \\u1ea2nh: <em>Ho&agrave;ng Th&ugrave;y.<\\/em><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">C\\u0169ng gi\\u1ed1ng b\\u1ea1n b&egrave; c&ugrave;ng trang l\\u1ee9a, Quang th&iacute;ch ch\\u01a1i  game. Nh\\u01b0ng l\\u1ecbch ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh trong bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1ed1i th\\u1ee9 b\\u1ea3y, khi m\\u1ecdi vi\\u1ec7c  h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp trong tu\\u1ea7n \\u0111&atilde; ho&agrave;n t\\u1ea5t. &Ocirc;ng L&ecirc; M\\u1ea1nh H&agrave; (b\\u1ed1 Quang) cho bi\\u1ebft, cho  con ch\\u01a1i nh\\u01b0ng l&uacute;c n&agrave;o &ocirc;ng c\\u0169ng ng\\u1ed3i b&ecirc;n c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 ki\\u1ec3m so&aacute;t.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">\\"Quang t\\u1eebng m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n b\\u1ecf h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111i ch\\u01a1i game n\\u0103m l\\u1edbp 8,  ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c t&ocirc;i quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh n\\u1ed1i m\\u1ea1ng v&agrave; cho ch&aacute;u ch\\u01a1i v&agrave;o cu\\u1ed1i tu\\u1ea7n,  d\\u01b0\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ec3m so&aacute;t c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u1edbn. B\\u1ed1 m\\u1eb9 kh&ocirc;ng ng\\u0103n c\\u1ea5m, nh\\u01b0ng ph\\u1ea3i lu&ocirc;n  b&ecirc;n c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 u\\u1ed1n n\\u1eafn con k\\u1ecbp th\\u1eddi\\", &ocirc;ng H&agrave; chia s\\u1ebb.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Khi b\\u1ed1 m\\u1eb9 v\\u1eafng nh&agrave;, Quang l&agrave; anh c\\u1ea3 n&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn vi\\u1ec7c  ch\\u0103m s&oacute;c em g&aacute;i \\u0111ang h\\u1ecdc l\\u1edbp 6. C\\u1eadu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111&aacute;nh gi&aacute; l&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ea3m \\u0111ang khi bi\\u1ebft  h\\u1ebft vi\\u1ec7c d\\u1ecdn d\\u1eb9p v&agrave; n\\u1ea5u n\\u01b0\\u1edbng. Nh\\u1eefng m&oacute;n ch\\u01b0a bi\\u1ebft l&agrave;m, Quang l&ecirc;n m\\u1ea1ng  t&igrave;m c&ocirc;ng th\\u1ee9c r\\u1ed3i in ra, th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n theo. M&oacute;n \\u0103n m&agrave; Quang l&agrave;m ngon nh\\u1ea5t  (theo \\u0111&aacute;nh gi&aacute; c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ed1 m\\u1eb9) l&agrave; m&oacute;n th\\u1ecbt l\\u1ee3n ba ch\\u1ec9 lu\\u1ed9c. Quang c&ograve;n l&agrave;m gia  s\\u01b0 cho em g&aacute;i hai m&ocirc;n To&aacute;n, ti\\u1ebfng Anh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Kh&ocirc;ng h\\u1ecdc L&yacute; ngay t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1edfi th\\u1eddi c\\u1ea5p 2, c\\u1eadu \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t  \\u0111am m&ecirc; m&ocirc;n To&aacute;n. B\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo\\u1eb7t ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi l\\u1edbp 8 Quang c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c thi \\u0111\\u1ed7 v&agrave;o  \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n h\\u1ecdc sinh gi\\u1ecfi 3 m&ocirc;n To&aacute;n, L&yacute;, H&oacute;a. Nh\\u01b0ng L&yacute; \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m cao nh\\u1ea5t  v&agrave; To&aacute;n l\\u1ea1i th\\u1ea5p nh\\u1ea5t n&ecirc;n b\\u1ed1 m\\u1eb9 m\\u1edbi khuy&ecirc;n Quang ch\\u1ecdn L&yacute; v&igrave; \\u0111&oacute; l&agrave; m&ocirc;n  h\\u1ecdc hay, nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ec5n v&agrave; c\\u0169ng l&agrave; m&ocirc;n c\\u1eadu h\\u1ecdc t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">\\"Sau m\\u1ed9t tu\\u1ea7n suy ngh\\u0129 ch&aacute;u m\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed3ng &yacute; h\\u1ecdc L&yacute; v&agrave; t\\u1eeb  l\\u1edbp 9 th&igrave; b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u01b0\\u1edbng theo m&ocirc;n n&agrave;y. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i lu&ocirc;n \\u1edf b&ecirc;n c\\u1ea1nh  \\u0111\\u1ed9ng vi&ecirc;n Quang ph&aacute;t huy nh\\u1eefng g&igrave; m&igrave;nh c&oacute;\\", b&agrave; Ph\\u1ea1m Th\\u1ecb Vi&ecirc;n (m\\u1eb9 Quang)  c\\u0169ng l&agrave; h\\u1ecdc sinh chuy&ecirc;n L&yacute; kh&oacute;a 1 c\\u1ee7a THPT Lam S\\u01a1n t&acirc;m s\\u1ef1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">B&agrave; Vi&ecirc;n cho bi\\u1ebft, gia \\u0111&igrave;nh nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tin Quang gi&agrave;nh  huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng V&agrave;ng Olympic V\\u1eadt l&yacute; ch&acirc;u &Aacute; t\\u1eeb th\\u1ea7y ch\\u1ee7 nhi\\u1ec7m v&agrave;o l&uacute;c n\\u1eeda \\u0111&ecirc;m  nh\\u01b0ng m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi v\\u1eabn h&eacute;t l&ecirc;n sung s\\u01b0\\u1edbng. B&agrave; h\\u01b0\\u1edbng cho Quang ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c  nghi&ecirc;n c\\u1ee9u V\\u1eadt l&yacute; sau khi t\\u1ed1t nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ea5p 3, c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 l&agrave; ng&agrave;nh n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng  \\u0111i\\u1ec7n ho\\u1eb7c n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7n nguy&ecirc;n t\\u1eed...<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Chia s\\u1ebb kinh nghi\\u1ec7m l&agrave;m b&agrave;i thi qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf, Quang n&oacute;i,  v&agrave;o ph&ograve;ng thi ph\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ec3 t&acirc;m tr\\u1ea1ng th\\u1eadt b&igrave;nh t\\u0129nh. \\"L&yacute; thuy\\u1ebft m&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng h\\u1ec1  thua k&eacute;m b\\u1ea1n, nh\\u01b0ng th\\u1ef1c h&agrave;nh th&igrave; c&oacute; ph\\u1ea7n y\\u1ebfu h\\u01a1n n&ecirc;n khi &ocirc;n ph\\u1ea3i ch&uacute; &yacute;  ph\\u1ea7n n&agrave;y, v&agrave;o thi c\\u0169ng ph\\u1ea3i l&agrave;m c\\u1ea9n th\\u1eadn\\", Quang n&oacute;i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Cu\\u1ed9c thi t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c \\u1edf \\u1ea4n \\u0110\\u1ed9, ngo&agrave;i kh&iacute; h\\u1eadu n&oacute;ng n\\u1ef1c, th\\u1ee9c  \\u0103n r\\u1ea5t cay n&ecirc;n Quang kh&oacute; c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 th&iacute;ch nghi. \\"Nh\\u1eefng ng&agrave;y \\u0111\\u1ea7u em c\\u1ed1 \\u0103n  cho c&oacute; s\\u1ee9c d&ugrave; l\\u1ea1 mi\\u1ec7ng. Nh\\u1eefng ng&agrave;y sau, \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; bi\\u1ebfn c\\u1ed1 n&agrave;o  v\\u1ec1 s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh thi, em \\u0103n m&igrave; t&ocirc;m mang theo t\\u1eeb nh&agrave;\\", Quang  cho hay.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><strong>Ho&agrave;ng Th&ugrave;y<\\/strong><\\/p>","introtext":"K&iacute;nh c\\u1eadn, th&ocirc;ng minh, h\\u1ecdc gi\\u1ecfi nh\\u01b0ng kh&ocirc;ng ph\\u1ea3i m\\u1ecdt  s&aacute;ch, gi&agrave;nh nhi\\u1ec1u th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch v\\u1ec1 th\\u1ec3 thao l&agrave; ch&acirc;n dung c\\u1ee7a L&ecirc; Huy Quang  (THPT chuy&ecirc;n Lam S\\u01a1n, Thanh H&oacute;a), ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi v\\u1eeba gi&agrave;nh huy ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng V&agrave;ng  Olympic V\\u1eadt l&yacute; ch&acirc;u &Aacute;.&gt; Vi\\u1ec7t Nam x\\u1ebfp th\\u1ee9 t\\u01b0 cu\\u1ed9c thi Olympic V\\u1eadt l&yacute; ch&acirc;u &Aacute;\\r\\nNheo m\\u1eaft sau c\\u1eb7p k&iacute;nh c\\u1eadn r\\u1ed3i n\\u1edf n\\u1ee5 c\\u01b0\\u1eddi t\\u01b0\\u01a1i r&oacute;i,  \\"ch&agrave;ng trai v&agrave;ng\\" c\\u1ee7a V\\u1eadt l&yacute; Vi\\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\\u1ebft, \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 cao  trong c&aacute;c k\\u1ef3 thi, c\\u1eadu ch\\u1ec9 c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t th\\u1ee9 v\\u0169 kh&iacute;, \\u0111&oacute; l&agrave; s\\u1ef1 ...","modified":"{\\"1337010082\\":\\"1\\"}"}', 1, 1337009893);
